These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, italian, australian, french
1. the italian is in an odd position##4
2. the french is between the dutch and the italian##2
3. the french is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | dutch | french | italian | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, blueberry, spinach, eggplant
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | blueberry | cucumber | eggplant | spinach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, adventure, fantasy, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
2. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching adventure movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | family | superhero | fantasy | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, sailing, handball
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
2. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | cricket | handball | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, rugby, climbing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | climbing | biathlon | rugby | golf |

