.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, mexican, german, australian
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the mexican is on the left or right of the australian##3
3. the german is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | german | russian | australian | mexican |

