1. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
2. the fan of country is between the fan of indie and the fan of dubstep##2
3. the fan of country is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | indie | country | dubstep |

