2. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is singing##2
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | board-games | singing | collecting | chess |

