.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, airplane, motorbike, ship
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | motorbike | airplane | ship | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, milk, soy-milk
1. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking tea##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | milk | tea | soy-milk |

