.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, cricket, climbing, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | climbing | snowboarding | cycling | cricket |

