.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, grapefruit, onion, cherry
1. the person eating grapefruit is the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
3. the person eating onion is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating spinach is in an even position##4
5. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | onion | cherry | grapefruit | spinach |

